==English==
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/pæn'di'ĭs'tĭk}}

===Alternative spellings===
*sometimes hyphenated or expressed as a phrase: '''pan-deistic''', '''pan deistic'''
*sometimes either the P or both the P and D are capitalized: '''Pandeistic''', '''PanDeistic'''
*variations of capitalization and spacing may be combined: '''Pan-deistic''', '''Pan-Deistic''', '''Pan Deistic''', '''Pan deistic'''
